."],"variants":[]},{"name":"le","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["1  ♂ ‘Profit’ or ‘sharp’.","2  ♀, ♂ ‘Upright’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When William le Prouz was born in 1215, in Chagford, Devon, England, United Kingdom, his father, Walter de Prouz, was 16 and his mother, Sara Dinham, was 12. He had at least 1 son and 1 daughter with Emma Widworthy. He died on 11 November 1270, in his hometown, at the age of 55."},"et":{"1215–11 November 1270":"1215–11. november 1270","1215–1270":"1215–1270","1266–Female":"1266–Surnud","1294–1316":"1294–1316","1310–1335":"1310–1335","1199–Male":"1199–Surnud","1203–Female":"1203–Surnud","11 November 1270":"11. november 1270","1316":"1316","1215":"1215","1203":"1203","1335":"1335","1310":"1310","1266":"1266","1199":"1199","1294":"1294","1270":"1270","Gidley Manor, Chagford, Okehampton, Devonshire, England":"Chagford, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Gidley Castle, Chagford, Okehampton, Devonshire, England":"Chagford, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1215–11 November 1270":"1215–11. marraskuuta 1270","1215–1270":"1215–1270","1266–Female":"1266–Kuollut","1294–1316":"1294–1316","1310–1335":"1310–1335","1199–Male":"1199–Kuollut","1203–Female":"1203–Kuollut","11 November 1270":"11. marraskuuta 1270","1316":"1316","1215":"1215","1203":"1203","1335":"1335","1310":"1310","1266":"1266","1199":"1199","1294":"1294","1270":"1270","Gidley Manor, Chagford, Okehampton, Devonshire, England":"Chagford, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Gidley Castle, Chagford, Okehampton, Devonshire, England":"Chagford, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1215–11 November 1270":"1215–11 novembre 1270","1215–1270":"1215–1270","1266–Female":"1266–Décédée","1294–1316":"1294–1316","1310–1335":"1310–1335","1199–Male":"1199–Décédé","1203–Female":"1203–Décédée","11 November 1270":"11 novembre 1270","1316":"1316","1215":"1215","1203":"1203","13